# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:17
translate chinese brandi7_75679cc4:

    # fd "Hey, [pcname]. I was just wondering if you wanted to go to this new ice cream place with me?"
    fd "嗨，[pcname]。我正想问你愿不愿意跟我去那家新开的冰淇淋店？"

