    # fd "See ya, [pcname]."
    fd "回头见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:25
translate chinese brandi7_733d8765:

    # pc "Bye Brandi."
    pc "再见，布兰迪。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:31
translate chinese brandi7_38b111e9:

    # fd "Okay, I'll meet you there. The place is called Cream Parlour. It's over close to Jackson Burger in that little strip mall there. Do you know what I'm talking about?"
    fd "好的，我在那里等你。那家店叫“Cream Parlour”。就在那个小型购物中心里，靠近杰克逊汉堡的地方。你知道我说的是哪里吗？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:32
translate chinese brandi7_04c7baf7:

    # pc "Yeah, I think so. I should be able to find it."
    pc "嗯，我想知道。我应该能找到。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:33
translate chinese brandi7_869b3860:

    # fd "Great. I'll see you there."
    fd "太好了。到时候见。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:37
translate chinese brandi7_66d3a0c0:

    # "I drive around the block a few times, looking for this place before I spot Brandi's fiery red hair as she walks into the front door."
    "我绕着街区转了几圈，正找这家店，突然看见布兰迪那头火红的头发，她正走进前门。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:38
translate chinese brandi7_27134b8b:

    # "The signs for the place are all small and I wouldn't have ever noticed it if she hadn't told me it was there."
    "店里的招牌都很小，要不是她提前告诉我，我根本不会注意到它。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:43
translate chinese brandi7_95a730d4:

    # "Brandi is waiting for me by the door when I walk in."
    "我一进门，布兰迪就在门口等着我。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:44
translate chinese brandi7_6fc3ba71:

    # fd "Hey, [pcname]. Glad you made it."
    fd "嘿，[pcname]。很高兴你来了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:45
translate chinese brandi7_0ee110c8:

    # fd "I already have my laptop set up over there, so let's get some ice cream."
    fd "我的笔记本电脑已经摆在那边了，咱们去买点冰淇淋吧。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:48
translate chinese brandi7_8786acba:

    # fd "Go ahead [pcname]. Order whatever you want."
    fd "你先点吧[pcname]。随便点什么都行。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:49
translate chinese brandi7_177587a1:

    # pc "I guess I'll go with a scoop of mint chocolate chip."
