# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:51
translate chinese brandi7_c78d82d1:

    # fd "I want a scoop of strawberry in a waffle cone and a banana on the side."
    fd "我要一球草莓味的装在华夫饼筒里，再配一根香蕉。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:52
translate chinese brandi7_4e9b27eb:

    # "Man" "A banana?"
    "Man" "香蕉？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:53
translate chinese brandi7_1a3633db:

    # fd "Yes. I'm sure you have bananas back there for banana splits right?"
    fd "是的。你们后面肯定有做香蕉船用的香蕉吧？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:54
translate chinese brandi7_b9afecaa:

    # "Man" "We do."
    "Man" "有的。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:55
translate chinese brandi7_972e1133:

    # fd "I just want the banana. I like bananas with ice cream, but I don't like the banana to touch the ice cream."
    fd "我只要香蕉。我喜欢香蕉配冰淇淋，但不喜欢香蕉碰到冰淇淋。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:56
translate chinese brandi7_1e075c69:

    # fd "I know it's weird."
    fd "我知道这有点奇怪。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:57
translate chinese brandi7_09af936b:

    # "Man" "However you like it miss."
    "Man" "小姐您喜欢怎样都可以。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:58
translate chinese brandi7_fea3a917:

    # fd "That's what I like to hear."
    fd "这就是我想听到的。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:61
translate chinese brandi7_d4195078:

    # fd "This looks really good."
    fd "这个看起来真不错。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:62
translate chinese brandi7_af423fc0:

    # pc "Yeah it does."
    pc "是啊。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:63
translate chinese brandi7_0c31dc5c:

    # fd "Okay, I'm going to unmute the chat now, so time to go into performance mode."
    fd "好了，我现在要把聊天静音取消，该进入表演模式了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:64
translate chinese brandi7_6c990091:

    # pc "Let's do it."
    pc "开始吧。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:67
translate chinese brandi7_d3883cc2:

    # fd "Hello everybody and welcome!"
    fd "大家好，欢迎收看！"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:68
translate chinese brandi7_bda69350:

    # fd "[pcname] is here with me again, on our second date. We're at a new ice cream parlor in Skyhill."
    fd "[pcname]又和我在一起了，这是我们的第二次约会。我们现在在Skyhill的一家新开的冰淇淋店。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:69
translate chinese brandi7_cc8a9142:

    # fd "Say hi, [pcname]."
    fd "跟大家打个招呼吧，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:70
translate chinese brandi7_89523da1:

    # pc "Hi everybody."
    pc "大家好。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:71
translate chinese brandi7_f1460d12:

    # fd "Okay, first taste, here we go."
    fd "好，第一口，来吧。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:74
translate chinese brandi7_4504ebee:

    # fd "Oh mine is really good. How's yours?"
    fd "哦，我的很好吃。你的怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:75
translate chinese brandi7_48398008:

    # pc "It's great."
    pc "很好吃。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:76
translate chinese brandi7_e0c06ef5:

    # fd "Can I have a taste? You can have some of mine too if you want."
    fd "我可以尝一口吗？如果你想的话，也可以尝尝我的。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:77
translate chinese brandi7_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "当然可以。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:81
translate chinese brandi7_ca265b29:

    # "I hold it over to her and she looks me directly in the eyes as she licks the ice cream in one long, smooth motion."
    "我把冰淇淋递向她，她直视着我的眼睛，用一个长而流畅的动作舔着冰淇淋。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:82
translate chinese brandi7_eecc364a:

    # "I'm almost positive she is thinking the same thing I am."
    "我几乎可以肯定，她想的和我一样。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:85
translate chinese brandi7_32a2e507:

    # fd "Oh yeah, yours tastes really good."
    fd "哦，是的，你的味道真好。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:86
translate chinese brandi7_ad822efd:

    # pc "You got a little bit of uh... "
    pc "你嘴角沾了一点……"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:87
translate chinese brandi7_f83e1eea:

    # fd "Oh, I got some of your cream on my lips?"
    fd "哦，我的嘴唇上沾了你的奶油？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:88
translate chinese brandi7_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "是的。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:89
translate chinese brandi7_80f63c56:

    # fd "Can't let that go to waste."
    fd "不能浪费啊。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:94
translate chinese brandi7_2e949ac6:

