    "她做了一个滑稽的表情，把嘴唇舔得干干净净。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:97
translate chinese brandi7_8d458a10:

    # fd "All right chat, give us a topic of conversation."
    fd "好了，聊天软件，给我们找个话题吧。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:98
translate chinese brandi7_baa02316:

    # fd "Oh come on, don't be gross."
    fd "哎呀别这样，别这么恶心。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:99
translate chinese brandi7_d0d5ac3c:

    # fd "Okay, that sounds like something good to talk about."
    fd "行，这听起来是个不错的聊天话题。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:102
translate chinese brandi7_7b894599:

    # fd "Where is the coolest place that you've ever been?"
    fd "你去过最酷的地方是哪里？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:103
translate chinese brandi7_6d6161a9:

    # pc "Well, I actually spent the last three years living in Brazil. So that was pretty cool."
    pc "其实，我过去三年一直住在巴西。那儿挺酷的。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:104
translate chinese brandi7_a6f52c72:

    # fd "Really? I love Brazil! The food there is amazing."
    fd "真的吗？我超爱巴西！那里的食物太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:105
translate chinese brandi7_e9fb365d:

    # fd "Feijoada, Picanha, Moqueca, Vatapa… all so delicious."
    fd "黑豆炖肉、皮坎哈牛排、莫克卡鱼汤、瓦塔帕……全都好吃极了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:106
translate chinese brandi7_79d7da7b:

    # pc "I don't know what any of that stuff is. I pretty much subsisted on empanadas and tacos the whole time."
    pc "我根本不知道那些是什么。我那段时间基本靠吃馅饼和墨西哥卷饼度日。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:107
translate chinese brandi7_6b23c9ee:

    # fd "Dude, you're killing me."
    fd "老兄，你真是要命。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:110
translate chinese brandi7_9ba3a748:

    # fd "Well, for me, it would probably be Paris."
    fd "对我来说，大概是巴黎吧。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:111
translate chinese brandi7_76cc9f92:

    # fd "I travelled all over with my family - Tokyo, Sydney, Rome, London, Brazil…"
    fd "我和家人去过很多地方——东京、悉尼、罗马、伦敦、巴西……"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:112
translate chinese brandi7_52cf29d8:

    # fd "But Paris was probably the best for me. Want to talk about delicious food? The pastries there, the chocolate, it's a whole different world."
    fd "但对我来说，巴黎大概是最棒的。要说美食吗？那里的糕点、巧克力，简直是另一个世界。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:115
translate chinese brandi7_4aac2e1b:

    # "We continue chit-chatting for a while, moving along to various subjects while eating until our ice cream is gone."
    "我们边吃边闲聊了一会儿，话题跳来跳去，直到冰淇淋吃完。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:116
translate chinese brandi7_f4f7d7d8:

    # fd "And now we have the banana."
    fd "现在轮到香蕉了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:117
translate chinese brandi7_968a29d0:

    # fd "My viewers love when I eat bananas."
    fd "我的观众最爱看我吃香蕉。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:118
translate chinese brandi7_278975f1:

    # pc "I wonder why?"
    pc "我猜这是为什么呢？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:121
translate chinese brandi7_56d348fc:

    # fd "If I deepthroat this banana right now, will you guys send in your tips?"
    fd "如果我现在把这根香蕉深喉下去，你们会打赏吗？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:122
translate chinese brandi7_57147408:

    # fd "If I pretend like this banana is a cock and just take the whole thing into my mouth?"
    fd "如果我假装这根香蕉是根鸡巴，直接把它整个塞进嘴里？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:123
translate chinese brandi7_7eff727a:

    # "I'm a bit taken aback by her forwardness here. Suddenly things take a very sexual turn. It's hot, but also a bit embarrassing. I can feel my face going flush."
    "她这般直白让我有点措手不及。气氛突然变得非常暧昧。虽然很刺激，但也有些尴尬。我能感觉到脸颊发烫。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:124
translate chinese brandi7_03a9fee7:

    # fd "All right, here we go."
    fd "好吧，开始吧。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:127
translate chinese brandi7_bfb572cd:

    # "She slowly slides the banana down her throat, easily taking it all the way in and holding it there."
    "她缓缓将香蕉滑入喉咙，轻松地吞下整根并停留在那里。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:128
translate chinese brandi7_a816a12c:

    # "Then she looks at me and smiles. God, I'm so hard right now."
    "接着她看着我笑了。天啊，我现在硬得不行。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:129
translate chinese brandi7_9433bc97:

    # "After a few moments, she slides the banana back out again."
    "过了一会儿，她又把香蕉滑了出来。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:132
translate chinese brandi7_aa82e575:

    # fd "Uh-oh. I think I broke him guys."
    fd "哎哟。我觉得我把他弄坏了，各位。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:133
translate chinese brandi7_8711297d:

    # fd "You okay over there, [pcname]?"
    fd "那边还好吗，[pcname]？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:134
translate chinese brandi7_36d337e5:

    # pc "Yes. Just very impressed."
    pc "没事。只是太惊讶了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:135
translate chinese brandi7_0c2e2dd4:

    # fd "What can I say? I REALLY like bananas."
    fd "我还能说什么呢？我真的超爱香蕉。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:138
translate chinese brandi7_d162bbe9:

    # "With that, she takes a big bite out of the end of the banana."
    "说完，她咬了香蕉尾部一大口。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:139
translate chinese brandi7_a7baf5bc:

    # "I reflexively cringe a bit."
    "我下意识地微微皱了皱眉。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:143
translate chinese brandi7_67423399:

    # "A few minutes later, we tell the chat goodbye and she closes the laptop."
    "几分钟后，我们跟聊天室道别，她合上了笔记本电脑。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:145
translate chinese brandi7_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/brandi_thanks2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/brandi_thanks2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:146
translate chinese brandi7_707c0e49:

    # fd "Thanks for hanging out with me and indulging my teasing. I have fun with you."
    fd "谢谢你陪我聊天，还包容我这些调侃。和你在一起我很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:147
translate chinese brandi7_30655a95:

    # pc "Yeah, you do."
    pc "是啊，确实。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:148
translate chinese brandi7_4e38c625:

    # fd "Don't worry, I'm looking forward to spending some time with your banana soon too."
    fd "别担心，我也期待很快能和你那根香蕉共度时光。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:149
translate chinese brandi7_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:150
translate chinese brandi7_d851d140:

    # fd "Yeah. I am. Really."
    fd "是啊。真的。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:155
translate chinese brandi7_4cedddd4:

    # "I lean in to kiss her, but she puts a finger on my lips and holds me back."
    "我凑过去想吻她，但她用手指按住我的嘴唇，拦住了我。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:156
translate chinese brandi7_e4d748ac:

    # fd "I want to. I really want to. But I want our first kiss to be on camera, for the audience."
    fd "我想吻你。我真的很想。但我希望我们的初吻能被镜头记录下来，献给观众。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:157
translate chinese brandi7_1307651b:

    # fd "Next time, okay?"
    fd "下次吧，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:158
translate chinese brandi7_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "好。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:159
translate chinese brandi7_c8fd64e0:

    # fd "People will love it. Seriously, it'll be great."
    fd "大家会喜欢的。真的，那会很棒。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:161
translate chinese brandi7_b15b8eff:

    # pc "Well, I better head out."
    pc "嗯，我该走了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:162
translate chinese brandi7_70e5ff1f:

    # fd "Yeah me too. Have a lot to do today."
    fd "是啊，我也是。今天还有好多事要做。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:165
translate chinese brandi7_69095e98:

    # fd "Thanks again, [pcname]. I really enjoy these little dates."
    fd "再次感谢你，[pcname]。我真的很喜欢这些小约会。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:166
translate chinese brandi7_1c4a6ce2:

    # pc "No problem. I do too."
    pc "没问题。我也是。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:167
translate chinese brandi7_380872a8:

    # fd "Okay. I'll call you for another one soon."
    fd "好的。我很快会打电话约你再见一次。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:168
translate chinese brandi7_0472b961:

    # pc "Looking forward to it."
    pc "期待那一天。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:171
translate chinese brandi7_8cebcc25:

    # "With that, we tell each other goodbye and head out to our cars."
    "说完这些，我们互相道别，走向各自的车。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi7.rpy:172
translate chinese brandi7_71a8f6e9:

    # "Man, she's so hot. I'm not sure about the whole internet audience thing, but she's so hot it might be worth the hassle."
    "天啊，她真性感。虽然对那个网络观众的事我有点拿不准，但她这么性感，可能值得我费点劲。"

